"Otherwise (the signal is trapped), only equality comparisons and explicit "
"conversions are silent. All other mixed operations raise "
":exc:`FloatOperation`."
msgstr "在其他情况下（即信号被捕获），则只静默执行相等性比较和显式转换。 所有其他混合运算都将引发 :exc:`FloatOperation`。"

